{"tid":1329433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港重光】日軍被市民毆打 大家的反應是 ……","createTime":"2019-07-18T08:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T05:12:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":542,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"fbd8555ea13e901ac59a79290ce85c3d4a182d93","tid":1329433,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:07:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JbRHKwZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJbRHKwZ.png&h=5fb77fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1945年8月，夏慤將軍率領英國的艦隊光復香港，英國人急於處理投降的日軍及收拾日軍留下的殘局；而一般市民則忙於收拾皇軍。<br />\n<br />\n受了三年零八個月的氣，市民在光復之後表現得十分勇武，落單的日軍及日本人被人毆打，認真港九新界冇得避。<br />\n<br />\n根據《香港光復那一天》記載，有市民在電車上發現了日本人，結果大家一擁而上，迫使那名日本人跳車逃生。當時市面仍有一些日本兵維持治安，被毆打的日本人向金鐘兵房外的日軍求救，日軍打算出手阻止之時，卻被前來的英軍向天鳴槍阻止。<br />\n<br />\n光復當天亦有指市民在海軍船埠外圍毆日本人，需要英國海軍陸戰隊前來解圍，可是已有一人被打死。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GgmxVh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GgmxVh&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=2cbda622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GgmxVh</a><br />\n<br />\n#予以強烈譴責<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n想睇更多香港的故事？<br />\nLike我哋的<br />\n【Facebook】<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/wetoasthk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwetoasthk&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=130affa5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/wetoasthk</a><br />\n【website】<a href=\"http://www.wetoasthk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=2fb5d89b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.wetoasthk.com</a><br />\n【IG】<a href=\"http://instagram.com/wetoasthk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fwetoasthk&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=87f0e359\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://instagram.com/wetoasthk</a>"},{"pid":"5376450c8fbef68fcd68a730da91163f125b303f","tid":1329433,"uid":22675,"like":1285,"dislike":11,"score":1274,"citedBy":18,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:08:41.000Z","msg":"日軍都有父母生，點解要咁對佢哋啊？有事唔好搵日軍幫手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本軍人只是日本軍國政府和香港人之間的磨心而已，而且日軍也有很多好人的。反對一切暴力的行為。"},{"pid":"b94dfe035d74a4c70351568716e1152cebad5360","tid":1329433,"uid":56015,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1963a7bd7573d2d1f0ee8c33b7352fb165cbf9a","tid":1329433,"uid":125680,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"quote":{"pid":"5376450c8fbef68fcd68a730da91163f125b303f","tid":1329433,"uid":22675,"like":1285,"dislike":11,"score":1274,"citedBy":18,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:08:41.000Z","msg":"日軍都有父母生，點解要咁對佢哋啊？有事唔好搵日軍幫手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本軍人只是日本軍國政府和香港人之間的磨心而已，而且日軍也有很多好人的。反對一切暴力的行為。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847750d269e8b029128a1f444b8adb808f1100c1","tid":1329433,"uid":22675,"like":194,"dislike":0,"score":194,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:09:34.000Z","msg":"點解唔試下用愛同和平感化佢地? 就算佢地殺左你全家，訴諸暴力就係錯，我予以最強力譴責<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1119587221482002/posts/2266596893447690?s=100002126184316&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1119587221482002%2Fposts%2F2266596893447690%3Fs%3D100002126184316%26sfns%3Dmo&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=42257b54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1119587221482002/posts/2266596893447690?s=100002126184316&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"c9eafec88868eddc2195e8c4ca85c